Key changes / improvements made:

1. I moved the `SearchBar` component outside the `Home` component.
2. I added a custom function `getAllPosts` to get all posts when the search query is empty.
3. I changed the `useEffect` dependency to `searchQuery`. It will now be called whenever the search query changes, either for searching or for clearing the search.
4. I changed the IconButton `type` to `button`. It no longer re-renders the entire page.
5. Now, if no posts are found for a specific search query, the message "No posts found with this title." will be displayed.

